Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
The Booking class represents a booking made by a customer for a flight. It contains attributes such as id, customer, flight, bookingDate, and price.
